snippet.textDisplay:
CSP: No more SOUND OF NATION
it is now ; "RYTHM OF UNITY" 
Literally the last visuals where everyone was dancing in their unique style and yet collectively looking so ONE THING, has my heart.  Such an immersive experience and such an overwhelming track.
This season has me thinking like Pakistan music scene is only going to go global but CSP is aiming something big something unthinkable and something spectacular. Seems like we are embarking upon a new journey to discover new soundscape, create new musical concepts and weave together other worldly compositions 
Can't wait to see see how it all plays out and how CSP gets the recognition and global spotlight for their contribution
